    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 3. Daten laden von FRED\n",
    "\n",
    "FRED stellt alle Zeitreihen als öffentlich abrufbare CSV-Dateien bereit – **ohne Account oder API-Key**.\n",
    "Der folgende Code lädt die drei Zeitreihen direkt aus dem Internet."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# FRED stellt Daten über eine direkte CSV-URL bereit:\n",
    "# Muster: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/graph/fredgraph.csv?id=SERIENNAME\n",
    "\n",
    "fred_url <- function(series_id) {\n",
    "  paste0(\"https://fred.stlouisfed.org/graph/fredgraph.csv?id=\", series_id)\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "# Daten herunterladen\n",
    "us_raw <- read.csv(fred_url(\"DTB3\"))\n",
    "eu_raw <- read.csv(fred_url(\"IR3TIB01DEM156N\"))\n",
    "fx_raw <- read.csv(fred_url(\"DEXUSEU\"))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Spaltennamen vereinheitlichen\n",
    "colnames(us_raw) <- c(\"date\", \"value\")\n",
    "colnames(eu_raw) <- c(\"date\", \"value\")\n",
    "colnames(fx_raw) <- c(\"date\", \"value\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Datumsformat setzen und fehlende Werte entfernen\n",
    "clean <- function(df) {\n",
    "  df %>%\n",
    "    mutate(date  = as.Date(date),\n",
    "           value = suppressWarnings(as.numeric(value))) %>%\n",
    "    filter(!is.na(value))\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "us_raw <- clean(us_raw)\n",
    "eu_raw <- clean(eu_raw)\n",
    "fx_raw <- clean(fx_raw)\n",
    "\n",
    "cat(\"Daten erfolgreich geladen!\\n\")\n",
    "cat(\"  US-Zinssatz (DTB3):              \", nrow(us_raw), \"tägliche Beobachtungen\\n\")\n",
    "cat(\"  EU-Zinssatz (IR3TIB01DEM156N):   \", nrow(eu_raw), \"monatliche Beobachtungen\\n\")\n",
    "cat(\"  Wechselkurs (DEXUSEU):           \", nrow(fx_raw), \"tägliche Beobachtungen\\n\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 4. Datenaufbereitung: Quartalswerte erstellen\n",
    "\n",
    "Die UIP-Analyse arbeitet **quartalsweise**: Wir vergleichen die Zinssätze **zu Beginn eines Quartals** (Jan, Apr, Jul, Okt) mit dem tatsächlichen Wechselkurs **am Ende desselben Quartals** (drei Monate später).\n",
    "\n",
    "**Warum Quartalsbeginn?** Weil ein Investor seine Entscheidung auf Basis der *heute beobachtbaren* Zinsen trifft."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Analysezeitraum\n",
    "start_date <- as.Date(\"2022-01-01\")\n",
    "end_date   <- as.Date(\"2026-03-31\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Hilfsfunktion: Monatsmittelwert bilden, dann Quartalsbeginn filtern\n",
    "to_quarterly <- function(df, varname) {\n",
    "  df %>%\n",
    "    filter(date >= start_date, date <= end_date) %>%\n",
    "    mutate(month_start = floor_date(date, \"month\")) %>%\n",
    "    group_by(month_start) %>%\n",
    "    summarise(value = mean(value, na.rm = TRUE), .groups = \"drop\") %>%\n",
    "    mutate(qstart = floor_date(month_start, \"quarter\")) %>%\n",
    "    filter(month_start == qstart) %>%          # nur erster Monat des Quartals\n",
    "    select(qstart, value) %>%\n",
    "    rename(!!varname := value)\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "us_q  <- to_quarterly(us_raw, \"i_US\")\n",
    "eu_q  <- to_quarterly(eu_raw, \"i_EU\")\n",
    "fx_q  <- to_quarterly(fx_raw, \"S_start\")   # Wechselkurs Quartalsanfang\n",
    "\n",
    "# Wechselkurs Quartalsende: erster Monat des *nächsten* Quartals = Ende des aktuellen\n",
    "fx_end_raw <- fx_raw %>%\n",
    "  filter(date >= start_date, date <= end_date + months(3)) %>%\n",
    "  mutate(month_start = floor_date(date, \"month\")) %>%\n",
    "  group_by(month_start) %>%\n",
    "  summarise(value = mean(value, na.rm = TRUE), .groups = \"drop\") %>%\n",
    "  mutate(qstart = floor_date(month_start, \"quarter\")) %>%\n",
    "  filter(month_start == qstart) %>%\n",
    "  mutate(qstart = qstart - months(3)) %>%    # dem Vorquartal zuordnen\n",
    "  select(qstart, value) %>%\n",
    "  rename(S_end = value)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Alle Variablen zusammenführen\n",
    "df <- us_q %>%\n",
    "  inner_join(eu_q,     by = \"qstart\") %>%\n",
    "  inner_join(fx_q,     by = \"qstart\") %>%\n",
    "  inner_join(fx_end_raw, by = \"qstart\") %>%\n",
    "  filter(!is.na(i_US), !is.na(i_EU), !is.na(S_start), !is.na(S_end))\n",
    "\n",
    "cat(\"Quartalsdatensatz erstellt:\", nrow(df), \"Quartale\\n\")\n",
    "cat(\"Zeitraum:\", format(min(df$qstart)), \"bis\", format(max(df$qstart)), \"\\n\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
