    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 7. UIP-Berechnung\n",
    "\n",
    "Jetzt wenden wir die UIP-Formel an:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$S_{t+1}^{\\text{UIP}} = S_t \\cdot \\frac{1 + i_{US}/400}{1 + i_{EU}/400}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Wir teilen durch **400**, weil: FRED-Zinsen sind in Jahresprozent → ÷100 für Dezimal → ÷4 für ein Quartal."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df <- df %>%\n",
    "  mutate(\n",
    "    # Zinsdifferenzial (Jahresbasis, Prozentpunkte)\n",
    "    zins_diff = i_US - i_EU,\n",
    "\n",
    "    # UIP-konformer Wechselkurs am Quartalsende\n",
    "    S_UIP = S_start * (1 + i_US / 400) / (1 + i_EU / 400),\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Tatsächliche Wechselkursänderung (%)\n",
    "    delta_s_actual = (S_end  / S_start - 1) * 100,\n",
    "\n",
    "    # UIP-vorhergesagte Änderung (%)\n",
    "    delta_s_uip    = (S_UIP  / S_start - 1) * 100,\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Abweichung: tatsächlich minus UIP-Prognose\n",
    "    abweichung     = delta_s_actual - delta_s_uip\n",
    "  )\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ergebnistabelle\n",
    "df %>%\n",
    "  mutate(Quartal = format(qstart, \"%Y Q%q\")) %>%\n",
    "  select(\n",
    "    Quartal,\n",
    "    `Zinsdiff. (PP)` = zins_diff,\n",
    "    `S Anfang`       = S_start,\n",
    "    `S UIP-Prognose` = S_UIP,\n",
    "    `S tatsächlich`  = S_end,\n",
    "    `Abweichung (%)` = abweichung\n",
    "  ) %>%\n",
    "  knitr::kable(digits = 4, align = \"lccccc\")"
   ]
  },
